PythonIDS
=========

Simple Python Based Intrusion Detection system. 

Dependency 1 
Flex 
http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/flex/flex-2.5.33.tar.gz?download

tar -xvzf flex-2.5.33.tar.gz

cd flex-2.5.33

PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/m4/bin/


./configure --prefix=/usr/local/flex

sudo make

sodo make install


Dependency =2
gcc compiler

Defalutly available in all linux version


Dependency ==3

Libpcap
